This project defines an XML document handler for creating, editing and
saving simple XML messages programmatically.

The entry point for using this project is the XMLDocument class.

See the TestXPathBasedDocument.java JUnit test case for an example of creating an XMLDocument instance.

See the GeMHa project for extensive use of XMLDocument objects, especially GenericMessageHandlerSettings.java,
ProcessMessageForDb.java and ProcessMessageForDbAction.java.
